claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table of contents and introductory text from an MMWR report, listing sections like Introduction, Methods, Vaccine Composition and Available Vaccines, and credits/attribution information for CDC and MMWR staff. It does not present any data or statements about Flublok or antigenic matching with WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains, and therefore does not support the claim.
